summary: Adds an enchanting table to breezehome.
descriptionHtml:
Hey guys this is my first modification to the game :), just something basic as having an enchanting table next to your bed!
feel free to leave comments about what you think about this :)

This mod focus on players that dont want new content like (home expansions) and want to stick with the original Skyrim with some improves :).

This was an old mod i upload to the steamworkshop and i decide to added to skyrimnexus.

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=9247
